        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Watering grape or berry bushes with certain alchemical liquids as they grow results in a ruby-red drink that\u2019s rich and heady. The vines develop a connection to their natural environment and impart it onto the wine\u2019s imbiber. For 1 minute after drinking a glass of arbor wine, you have tremorsense at a range of 30 feet.",
